aboutPageWhoWeAreContent.en-US:
Cialfo started in 2012/2014/2017 with one mission: to increase transparency and accessibility of college information. 

Our team is made up of former college counselors, educators, and technology professionals working to change how the world approaches post-secondary education. And our platform emerges from the real world experiences of those we serve, whether they’re a devoted counselor or a steadfast principal.
